      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "UNMASKED (4) hit the ground running and never headed to claim a maiden victory two back then finished a 8 length seventh last start at this track over 352m (20.47). Returns to the scene of his maiden win. Key player on best and worth another chance. JAG THE JOKER (1) is suited by the inside draw. Last start finished 6th over 300m at Q Straight beaten 3.5 lengths (17.03) behind Kicker Wildcard in a Grade 6 on February 23. Can hit the frame with the right run. TAHITIAN STAR (2) turned in a plain run last time when seventh at Q Straight over 350m behind Boney Maloney (19.63) in a Grade 6. Was in the money the start prior. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from four attempts. Should be about the money. KOALA CLAWS (8) is in the mix following a brief let-up.",
